  cases' id r with rs
  · cases' id l with ls ll lx lr
    · exact ι x
    · cases' id ll with lls
      · cases' lr with _ _ lrx
        · exact node 2 l x nil
        · exact node 3 (ι lx) lrx ι x
      · cases' id lr with lrs lrl lrx lrr
        · exact node 3 ll lx ι x
        · exact
